  "3256960": {
    "name": "SynthetiCell BioClicker",
    "steam_appid": 3256960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个迷人的增量模拟游戏中，管理资源、创造生命并确保数千个合成细胞群落的生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受到著名数学家约翰·霍顿·康威（John Horton Conway）的“生命游戏”的启发，其中细胞根据 4 条基本规则生存或死亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这场“放置革命”挑战您作为玩家实现稳定和繁荣的生态系统以确保物种繁衍，否则您将屈服于进化的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/96e9a39796d18764d5b651acc207402a.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>点击等于生命：</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要环境条件最佳。观察你的殖民地成长和扩张，但不要坐以待毙，要升级你的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/456e8fe7675a47c050464a40a00c07d5.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>大自然是残酷的：</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心！此外，与所有生物体一样，恶性细胞也会产生，它们会试图自我克隆并扩散，以摧毁整个菌落。尽快提高你的防御技能来对抗它们并保护物种。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/acb5661a7ab30722413c3c69df56989f.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/acb5661a7ab30722413c3c69df56989f.webm?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/acb5661a7ab30722413c3c69df56989f.mp4?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>生物采矿或死亡：</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果得不到必需的元素，蜂群就会死亡！进入多细胞生物的内部，探索和收集对于化学键形成至关重要的分子，没有这些分子，生命就不可能存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5ed82895de2858fb19f7797abcd8a824.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >增强纳米机器人细胞分子收集器和免疫防御系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/27281ecf7e0503d5ad8ec79731273f38.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>有时候拥有资源并不意味着一切！</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 完美地组合一长串化学元素不是一项容易记忆或复制的任务，但这对于殖民地的繁荣是必要的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/deebf82719d038bc8eb46c9ab34d8acf.avif?t=1745050479\" width=800 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>奖励活动：</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过随机迷你游戏赚取更多额外的“硬币”来提高您的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/18daa885ea89a379f2f1e87d4279b36d.avif?t=1745050479\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras_big/18daa885ea89a379f2f1e87d4279b36d.avif?t=1745050479 width=800 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SynthetiCell BioClicker 展示了简单系统如何产生令人惊讶的复杂性，激发了许多领域的新研究和应用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5f9f42a22519a319e4b580700d2a6f93.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5f9f42a22519a319e4b580700d2a6f93.webm?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/5f9f42a22519a319e4b580700d2a6f93.mp4?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用[b]约翰·霍顿·康威 (John Horton Conway) 的 4 条规则[/b]形成的惊人模式的真实例子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/003465bddb450c93cad5b6a386e3b9ee.apng?t=1745050479\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/003465bddb450c93cad5b6a386e3b9ee.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" class=\"bb_img\" width=89 height=145 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/838a5cc66e0456d2c55991b92c649846.apng?t=1745050479\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/838a5cc66e0456d2c55991b92c649846.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" class=\"bb_img\" width=137 height=137 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/661f815ca07c5c48d8508424e5e63dcc.poster.avif?t=1745050479\" width=126 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/661f815ca07c5c48d8508424e5e63dcc.webm?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/661f815ca07c5c48d8508424e5e63dcc.mp4?t=1745050479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256960/extras/08c2a5fb2d91fd86bc1768544e1f4347.avif?t=1745050479\" width=84 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入这次生物合成体验，探索一个每次点击都很重要的世界！</p>",
